{"tid":173650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實曾俊華都好慘","createTime":"2017-03-26T10:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T12:28:41.000Z","uid":16970,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba6820b82950454a4df0bda65e155b27421cfca","tid":173650,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"曾俊華啲擁躉見到咁嘅投票結果，會唔會為佢地心目中最理想嘅特首企出嚟抗爭，宣佈唔接受依個投票結果呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果班擁躉都係默默接受結果，咩都唔會做嘅，我就真係唔知曾俊華之前落區拍片搞咁多嘢係為乜，因為依啲嘢冇為佢增加那怕係一張選票。<br />\n<br />\n而依啲所謂「擁躉」，好多都只係純粹搭一部聲稱係「民意」嘅順風車，發覺部車爆軚就落車截過部，唔會同部車產生任何感情。<br />\n<br />\n其實曾俊華都好慘。"},{"pid":"ccc106e6c1029769a755cd7ef810eecc5f88d064","tid":173650,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37465afd583f5014a1b571f9cfbda3741f456263","tid":173650,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"睇完我仲以為市民有份投<br />\n咪扮民意啦"},{"pid":"8d5c84b8bd93106e606805ea352d29f5f2756abb","tid":173650,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:16:55.000Z","msg":"抗咩爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話啲票有問題都話, 規則係咁輸咗有咩好講"},{"pid":"670fe90f56ef12132fe0388c3e7e502319eb8db7","tid":173650,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5772afc28c355c0fdeb341b963116c74ba407514","tid":173650,"uid":89768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾俊華啲擁躉見到咁嘅投票結果，會唔會為佢地心目中最理想嘅特首企出嚟抗爭，宣佈唔接受依個投票結果呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果班擁躉都係默默接受結果，咩都唔會做嘅，我